title: Zach Galifianakis Returns
description:
Comedian Zach Galifianakis feels…sincere about being Conan O’Brien’s friend.


 

Zach sits down with Conan once again to discuss comedy bits to do in a restaurant, cultivating a certain kind of rudeness, and little-known historical facts. Later, Matt Gourley seeks Conan’s guidance on raising a red-headed child.


 

Got a question for Conan? Call our voicemail: (323) 451-2821.

 

 

For Conan videos, tour dates and more visit TeamCoco.com.
author: conaf@teamcoco.com (Team Coco & Earwolf)
